    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214180/extras/7c166adf2beedc47022d805cad78b202.avif?t=1729022873\" width=600 height=178 /></span>Explore and uncover the Spooky Mysteries surrounding Grimfield in this Action Adventure! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214180/extras/45cf495f18de15b981f45a5f5908db28.webp?t=1729022873\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214180/extras/45cf495f18de15b981f45a5f5908db28.poster.avif?t=1729022873\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=100 /></picture></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About Grimfield</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grimfield is a small town that has drawn attention by mysterious and unexplained events that have recently taken place there.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As Lucas’ parents are in love with everything related to the paranormal, the family traveled to Grimfield’s forest to investigate…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214180/extras/4aea996851299e7190ffca7e5fb198ed.poster.avif?t=1729022873\" width=600 height=409 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214180/extras/4aea996851299e7190ffca7e5fb198ed.webm?t=1729022873\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Amulet</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >On their way to Grimfield, a mysterious object was given to them, an antique amulet…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This magic amulet summons a magic hand that becomes an extension of Lucas, allowing him to activate and grab elements far from him!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214180/extras/0702c972f087ded515841c3864630be3.poster.avif?t=1729022873\" width=600 height=674 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214180/extras/0702c972f087ded515841c3864630be3.webm?t=1729022873\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214180/extras/0702c972f087ded515841c3864630be3.mp4?t=1729022873\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unique action gameplay with a floating magic hand mechanique!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Great 3D + 2D Cartoonish Art style!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mysterious adventure!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Awesome OST!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214180/extras/78244652228a7e3a8712971deb334536.avif?t=1729022873\" width=600 height=245 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Nachon Lab</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ogre Pixel</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2023</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
